tool_description: Sempico provides services for A2P SMS mailings around the world, HLR/MNP Lookup services, and is also the developer of the multifunctional SMPP platform Gatum. We also provide a convenient API to integrate the service for sending SMS into any software.
name: Sempico Solutions SMS
title: Sempico Solutions SMS

api_list.name: Log out (delete token)
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://sempico-solutions-sms.p.rapidapi.com/v1/logout"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "sempico-solutions-sms.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
